::Prowl/Striker::

Prowl smiles slightly at Iron Raptor's comment, and a slight thrill runs 
through his body as she touches his shoulder. He looks at her, trying to 
figure out why his body had responded so to her touch. He shakes the feeling 
off.

"If heroic behavior was not common, I'd be dead by now. Let's go check if 
anyone else is injured." Prowl says and walks off toward the exit.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker opens his eyes and groans. He sits up, realizing that that was not a 
good idea. His stomach twists and mechfluid flows out of his mouth all over 
the furs covering him. He falls back to the ground, breathing heavily and 
finally falling unconcious again.
